dct_title_s: Insurance maps of the New Jersey coast : volume 2
dct_description_sm: Includes key, key maps, index to sheet numbers and text. Series includes maps of Asbury Park, Avon by the Sea, Belmar, Deal Beach, Loch Arbour, Manasquan, Neptune City, Ocean Grove, Ocean Park, Sea Girt and Spring Lake Beach. Title sheet; map sheets foldered separately under name of town.
dct_publisher_sm: New York : Sanborn-Perris Map Co., Limited, 1890.
